data.description: NEW IMPROVED PRICE!!! LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION!  AMAZING OPPORTUNITY TO OWN RARE RR2, DIVIDABLE ACREAGE IN FLORENCE! SPLIT OFF 2 ACRES AND BUILD YOUR DREAM HOME! Fantastic potential with this diamond in the rough. Tucked back off Hwy 101 sits a thoughtfully designed ranch style home with two living spaces with both a wood stove and a fireplace. Primary bedroom has en suite bathroom, walk-in closet, plus adjoining hot tub area that opens to back deck. Backyard oasis boasts a beautiful, newer wrap-around deck with built-in seating. Take in the sights and sounds of nature with terraced grounds and your own pond! Head down to the lower area of the terraced yard where it's perfect for family campouts, lawn games and a firepit, OR build your dream shop! Roof and decks only a few years old. Tons of flat parking to host guests, RV's, ATV's and boats! Build on two acres and turn existing home into a perfect vacation rental for folks to enjoy the sand dunes, river, lakes, kayaking, hiking, fishing, crabbing and more! Minutes to Heceta Head Lighthouse, Sea Lion Caves, Old Town Florence, Three Rivers Casino, Siuslaw River, Honeyman State Park and the coveted Sand Dunes of Florence. Enjoy lake activities like fishing and kayaking on the nearby Woahink and Siltcoos. So much room and potential for an income property or family compound. Seller is negotiable on the fishing boat!
